# Steps

Progress indicator for multi-step flows.

## Basic Usage
::TuffDemo{title="Steps" description="Show progress across steps." code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxSteps :active="1">
      <TxStep title="Start" description="Collect basics" :step="0" />
      <TxStep title="Details" description="Fill in details" :step="1" />
      <TxStep title="Finish" description="Review and submit" :step="2" />
    </TxSteps>
  </template>
---
#preview
<tx-steps :active="1">
  <tx-step title="Start" description="Collect basics" :step="0" />
  <tx-step title="Details" description="Fill in details" :step="1" />
  <tx-step title="Finish" description="Review and submit" :step="2" />
</tx-steps>
:::

